(1, 'Operatii cu vectori', '2015-04-03', 'Vladutu Loredana', 't', 'operatii, vectori', '<p>\r\nSe citeste un vector <b>v</b> cu <b>n</b> elemente numere intregi. <br><br>\r\nSe declara: int v[100], n; <br><br>\r\nCerinte: <br><br>\r\n1. Citirea si afisarea unui vector\r\n<br><br>\r\n2. Afisarea in ordine inversa a elementelor unui vector\r\n<br><br>\r\n3. Suma elementelor unui vector\r\n<br><br>\r\n4. Produsul elementelor unui vector\r\n<br><br>\r\n5. Media aritmetica a elementelor unui vector\r\n<br><br>\r\n6. Stergerea unui element egal cu o valoare data x\r\n<br><br>\r\n7. Stergerea elementului de pe pozitia k\r\n<br><br>\r\n8. Inserarea unui element pe pozitia k\r\n</p>', 'Vectori', 'Oryx Antelope16.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2, 'Algoritmi fundamentali de prelucrare a vectorilor', '2015-03-24', 'Vladutu Loredana', 'Dock1.jpg', 'algoritmi, prelucrare, vectori', '<p>1. Cautare secventiala\r\n<br>\r\n2. Cautare binara\r\n<br>\r\n3. Interclasare \r\n<br>\r\n4. Metode de sortare (Interschimbare, Metoda bulelor)</p>', 'Vectori', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3, 'Cautare secventiala', '2015-04-23', 'Vladutu Loredana', 'secventiala16.jpg', 'cautare secventiala', '<p>Cautarea secventiala presupune parcurgerea secventiala a unui tablou unidimensional si compararea fiecarui element din tablou cu elementul cautat pana cand acesta este gasit sau se ajunge la sfarsitul tabloului.</p>\r\n<p> <span style="font-family: Arial, Arial; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14pt;">Se da vectorul<b> v </b>cu <b>n</b> elemente:</span>  </p>\r\n<p><b>v[0]    v[1]    v[2]  ...  v[n-2]    v[n-1]  </b>  </p> \r\n<p> Sa se verifice daca o valoare <b>x</b> se gaseste printre elementele vectorului <b>v</b>.  </p>\r\n<p> Se presupune ca <b>x</b> nu se gaseste in vector. Se foloseste variabila de control <b>ok</b>.  </p>\r\n<p>Initial ok=0. In momentul in care x se gaseste printre elementele vectorului <b>ok=1</b>.   </p>\r\n<p>Pentru a vedea parcurgerea programului de cautare secventiala, dati click pe butonul "Cautare secventiala".</p>\r\n<script type="text/javascript">\r\n\r\n function add_textbox()\r\n {\r\n  var element,n,i,ob,v,x,k,ok;\r\n  v = new Array(10);\r\n  k = 0;\r\n  ok = 0;\r\n  n=parseInt(prompt("Introduceti o valoare pentru n="));\r\n  \r\n  if(n>15)\r\n     alert("Numar prea mare.");\r\n  else\r\n   for(i=0;i<n;i++)\r\n   {\r\n    v[i]=parseInt(prompt("Introduceti o valoare pentru v[" + i + "]="));\r\n    caseta = document.createElement("input"); \r\n    caseta.setAttribute("type", "text");\r\n    caseta.setAttribute("value",v[i]);\r\n    caseta.setAttribute("size",5);\r\n    caseta.style.background="lime";\r\n    ob = document.getElementById("vector"); \r\n    ob.appendChild(caseta);\r\n    \r\n   } x=parseInt(prompt("Introduceti o valoare pentru x="));\r\n    for(i=0;i<n;i++){ if(x==v[i]){ok=ok+1;\r\n	k=i+1;}  }\r\n   if(ok==1){\r\ncaseta = document.createElement("input"); \r\n    caseta.setAttribute("type", "text");\r\n    caseta.setAttribute("value","S-a gasit numarul pe pozitia "+k+" ");\r\n    caseta.setAttribute("size",50);\r\n    caseta.style.background="lightblue";\r\n    ob = document.getElementById("vector"); \r\n    ob.appendChild(caseta);}else {caseta = document.createElement("input"); \r\n    caseta.setAttribute("type", "text");\r\n    caseta.setAttribute("value","Nu s-a gasit "+ x + " in vector!");\r\n    caseta.setAttribute("size",20);\r\n    caseta.style.background="lightblue";\r\n    ob = document.getElementById("vector"); \r\n    ob.appendChild(caseta);}\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</script>\r\n<span id="vector"><input type="submit" value="Cautare secventiala" onClick="add_textbox()"><br> </span><br /> \r\n\r\n<p> Algoritmul este:<br />\r\n<b>   i&#8592;0 OK&#8592;0 <br /></b>\r\n<b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cat timp (i < n && OK==0) <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;daca(x==v[i]) OK&#8592;1;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;altfel i&#8592;i+1 (i creste)<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sfarsit daca<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sfarsit cat timp </b><br />\r\nExemplu N=6<br />\r\n <br />\r\n<img src="images/$img1"> <br>\r\n<p>Variabila de control <b>OK=0</b> si valoarea <b>X=12</b> ,apoi ii dam valoarea zero unui contor de exemplu <b>i=0</b>  </p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nVerificam: <b>i=0<6 (A) && OK==0 (A)<br> x==V[0] (10) (F) <br> i=0+1 <br>Se reia cautarea<br>\r\ni=2<6 (A) && OK==0 (A)<br> x==V[1] (20) (F) <br> i=1+1 <br>Se reia cautarea<br><br>\r\ni=2<6 (A) && OK==0 (A)<br> x==V[2] (15) (F) <br> i=2+1 <br>Se reia cautarea<br><br>\r\ni=3<6 (A) && OK==0 (A)<br> x==V[3] (30) (F) <br> i=3+1 <br>Se reia cautarea<br><br>\r\ni=4<6 (A) && OK==0 (A)<br> x==V[4] (12) (A) => OK==1 <br>Se reia cautarea<br><br>\r\ni=4<6 (A) && OK==0 (F) ; Se iese din structura cat timp si se termina cautarea.</b>\r\n </p>\r\n\r\n<p> <b>Secventa in C++</b> </p>\r\n<textarea rows="10" cols="50" readonly style="color: lightblue; background-color: grey; width: 350px; height: 200px;">  \r\ni=ok=0;\r\nwhile(i<n&&!ok)\r\n    \r\n      if(x==v[i]) ok=1;\r\n        else i++;\r\n    \r\nif(ok) \r\n  cout<<x<<" se gaseste in vector";\r\nelse \r\n  cout<<x<<" nu se gaseste in vector";\r\n</textarea>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Vectori', 'Algoritmi fundamentali de prelucrare a vectorilor', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4, 'Cautare binara', '2015-03-29', 'Vladutu Loredana', 'binara_132.jpg', 'cautare binara', '<p>Fie vectorul <u>v</u> cu <u>n</u> elemente <u>ordonate crescator</u> si <u>x</u> o valoare data. Sa se verifice daca <u>x</u> se gaseste in vectorul <u>v</u>.</p>\r\n<p><u>Se aplica algoritmul:</u><br>\r\n\r\nst&#8592; 0; dr&#8592; n-1; ok&#8592;0;\r\n<br>cat timp(st< =dr && ok=0)\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; m&#8592;[(st+dr)/2]\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;daca x=v[m] atunci ok&#8592;1\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;altfel\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;daca x< v[m] atunci\r\n &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n//situatia_1\r\n\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;dr&#8592; m-1\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;altfel\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  \r\n//situatia_2\r\n\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;st&#8592;m+1\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sfarsit_daca\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sfarsit_daca\r\n<br>sfarsit_cat_timp<br>\r\n<br>&nbsp;daca ok=1 atunci \r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;scrie x, "_se gaseste in vector"\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;altfel\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;scrie x, "_nu se gaseste in vector"\r\n<br>sfarsit_daca</b>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p> situatia_1 <br>\r\n<table style="width:334; height:29; border:1px solid black; " >  \r\n<tr>\r\n              <th style="width:35px; height:23px; border:1px solid black;"  scope="col">...<th>\r\n              <th style="width:35px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">v[st]</th>\r\n              <th style="width:35px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">...</th>\r\n              <th style="width:30px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">x</th>\r\n              <th style="width:30px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">...</th>\r\n              <th style="width:30px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">v[m]</th>\r\n              <th style="width:30px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">...</th>\r\n              <th style="width:35px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">v[dr]</th>\r\n              <th style="width:35px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">...</th>\r\n            </tr>\r\n          </table></p>\r\n<p> situatia_2 <br> \r\n<table style="width:334; height:29; border:1px solid black; " >   \r\n<tr>\r\n              <th style="width:35px; height:23px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">...</th>\r\n              <th style="width:35px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">v[st]</th>\r\n              <th style="width:35px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">...</th>\r\n              <th style="width:30px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">v[m]</th>\r\n              <th style="width:30px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">...</th>\r\n              <th style="width:30px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">x</th>\r\n              <th style="width:30px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">...</th>\r\n              <th style="width:35px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">v[dr]</th>\r\n              <th style="width:35px; border:1px solid black;" scope="col">...</th>\r\n            </tr>\r\n          </table></p>\r\n<h1> Explicatii: </h1>\r\n<p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li> Cautarea lui <b>x</b> se face printre elementele ordonate crescator <b>v[st]</b>, <b>v[st+1]</b>, <b>...</b>, <b>v[dr-1]</b>, <b>v[dr]</b>.</li>\r\n <li> Initial , <b>st=0</b> si <b>dr=n-1</b>, iar variabila de control <b>ok=0</b> (x nu se gaseste in vector)\r\n<li> Cautarea se efectueaza cat timp sunt indeplinite simultan conditiile:\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;- <b>st&#8592;dr</b> (mai sunt de verificat elemente posibil a fi egale cu x)\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;- <b>ok=0</b> (nu s-a gasit x in vector)\r\n<li> In situatia in care conditiile sunt adevarate se verifica daca <b>x=v[m]</b>, unde <b>m=[(st+dr)/2]</b>\r\n<li> Daca este adevarata aceasta conditie , atunci <b>ok=1</b> si se va opri cautarea.\r\n<li> Daca este falsa aceasta conditie, se continua  cautarea astfel:\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;- <b>x< v[m]</b> atunci <u>x</u> se va cauta in stanga lui <u>v[m]</u>. Deci, <u>dr=m-1</u>.\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;- <b>x> v[m]</b> atunci <u>x</u> se va cauta in dreapta lui <u>v[m]</u>. Deci, <u>st=m+1</u>.\r\n<li> Exista doua situatii cand se poate oprii cautarea:\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;- <b>st> dr</b>, adica nu mai exista elemente pozitive a fi egale cu x\r\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;- <b>ok=1</b>, adica x se gaseste in vector.</ul>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>Exemplu: </h4>  \r\nn=9&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;x=20<br>\r\n<img src="images/$img1">\r\n  <br>\r\nst=0&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;dr=8&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ok=0\r\n<br> st<dr && ok=0 (0<8 && 0=0) Adevarat\r\n<br> m=[(st+dr)/2]=[(0+8)/2]=4\r\n<br> x=v[m] (20=15) Fals\r\n<br> Pentru x > v[m] (20>15) => Se continua cautarea in dreapta lui v[m]. Deci, st=m+1=4+1=5. <br><br>\r\n <img src="images/$img2">\r\n<br>\r\nst<dr && ok=0 (5<8 && 0=0) Adevarat\r\n<br> m=[(st+dr)/2]=[(5+8)/2]=6\r\n<br> x=v[m] (20=31) Fals\r\n<br> Pentru ca x< v[m] (20<31) => Se continua cautarea in stanga lui v[m]. Deci, dr=m-1=6-1=5.<br><br>\r\n<img src="images/$img3">\r\n<br>\r\nst<dr && ok=0 (4<5 && 0=0) Adevarat\r\n<br> m=[(st+dr)/2]=[(4+5)/2]=4\r\n<br>x=v[m] (20=15) Fals\r\n<br> Pentru ca x>v[m] (20>15) => Se continua cautarile in dreapta lui v[m]. Deci, st=m+1=4+1=5. <br><br>\r\n<img src="images/$img4">\r\n<br>\r\nst<dr && ok=0 (5<5 && 0=0) Adevarat\r\n<br> m=[(st+dr)/2]=[(5+5)/2]=5\r\n<br> x=v[m] (20=20) Adevarat => ok=1\r\n<br> st< dr && ok=0 (5<5 && 1=0) Fals\r\n<br> Se opreste cautarea intrucat <b>ok=1</b>, deci <u>x</u> se gaseste in vector.\r\n<br> <BR><div class=test3><B>Secventa in C++</B></div> <br>\r\n<textarea rows="10" cols="50" readonly style="color: lightblue; background-color: grey; width: 300px; height: 150px;">  \r\nst=0; dr=n-1; ok=0;\r\nwhile(st<=dr&&ok==0)\r\n     {m=(st+dr)/2;\r\n        if(x==v[m])\r\n          ok=1;\r\n         else\r\n           if(x<v[m])\r\n             dr=m-1;\r\n         else\r\n             st=m+1;\r\n     }\r\nif(ok==1) cout<<"x se gaseste in vector";\r\nelse cout<<"x nu se gaseste in vector"; \r\n</textarea>', '', 'binara_267.jpg', 'binara_377.jpg', 'binara_461.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Vectori', 'Algoritmi fundamentali de prelucrare a vectorilor', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(5, 'Operatii cu matrici', '2015-03-30', 'Vladutu Loredana', 'Tree81.jpg', 'operatii, matrici', '<p>\r\nSe citeste matricea <b>A</b> cu <b>m</b> linii si <b>n</b> coloane, iar elementele sunt numere intregi.\r\n<br /><br />\r\nSe declara: A[100][100], m, n;\r\n<br /><br />\r\n Sa se efectueze urmatoarele operatii:\r\n<br /><br />\r\n1. Citirea si afisarea matricei\r\n<br /><br />\r\n2. Suma si produsul elementelor matricei\r\n<br /><br />\r\n3. Suma si produsul elementelor fiecarei linii din matrice\r\n<br /><br />\r\n4. Suma si produsul elementelor fiecarei coloane din matrice\r\n<br /><br />\r\n5. Maximul elementelor matricei si numarul sau de aparitii\r\n<br /><br />\r\n6. Minimul elementelor matricei si numarul sau de aparitii\r\n<br /><br />\r\n7. Maximul elementelor fiecarei linii\r\n<br /><br />\r\n8. Minimul elementelor fiecarei linii\r\n<br /><br />\r\n9. Maximul elementelor fiecarei coloane\r\n<br /><br />\r\n10. Minimul elementelor fiecarei coloane\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n</p>', 'Matrici', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(6, 'Matrici patratice', '2015-04-23', 'Vladutu Loredana', 'PATRAT173.jpg', 'patrici, patrat, patratice', '<p>\r\nO <b>matrice patratica</b> este o matrice in care numarul liniilor este egal cu numarul coloanelor. Lungimea logica a unei matrice patrate este <b>n x n</b> (unde <b>n</b>= numarul de linii si de coloane). Ea este impartita in zone, de cele doua diagonale : \r\n<ul>\r\n<li>diagonala principala ; </li>\r\n<li>diagonala secundara . </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Diagonala principala :</b>\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="images/$img2"> <br /><br /><br />\r\n<b>Diagonala secundara :</b>\r\n<img src="images/$img3">\r\n</p>', 'Matrici', 'PATRAT18.jpg', 'PATRAT227.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(7, 'Citirea si afisarea unui vector', '2015-03-27', 'Vladutu Loredana', 'citire1.jpg', 'citire, vector, citirea', '<p>\r\n#include &#60;iostream&#62 <br>\r\nusing namespace std; <br>\r\nint main () <br>\r\n{<img src="images/$img1" style="float:right;"><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int v[100];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int n,i;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"n="; cin>>n;<br>\r\n//se citesc elementele vectorului <br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0;i&#60;n;i++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;{<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"v["&#60;&#60;i&#60;&#60;"]=";<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cin>>v[i];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"Elementele vectorului sunt:"&#60;&#60;endl;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0;i&#60;n;i++) <br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;v[i]&#60;&#60;" "; <br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;return 0; <br>\r\n} \r\n</p>', '', 'Frangipani Flowers51.jpg', 'Winter Leaves29.jpg', 'Toco Toucan53.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Vectori', 'Operatii cu vectori', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(8, 'Afisarea in ordine inversa a elementelor unui vector', '2015-03-27', 'Vladutu Loredana', 'inversa3.jpg', 'afisare, elemente, vector', '<p>\r\n#include &#60;iostream&#62 <br>\r\nusing namespace std; <br>\r\nint main ( ) <br>\r\n{<img src="images/$img1" style="float:right;"><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int v[100];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int n,i;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"n="; cin>>n;<br>\r\n//se citesc elementele vectorului <br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0;i&#60;n;i++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;{<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"v["&#60;&#60;i&#60;&#60;"]=";<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cin>>v[i];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"Elementele vectorului in ordine inversa sunt:"&#60;&#60;endl;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=n-1;i&#62;=0;i--) <br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;v[i]&#60;&#60;" "; <br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;return 0; <br>\r\n} \r\n</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Vectori', 'Operatii cu vectori', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(9, 'Suma elementelor unui vector', '2015-03-27', 'Vladutu Loredana', 'suma12.jpg', 'suma, elemente, vector', '<p>\r\n#include &#60;iostream&#62 <br>\r\nusing namespace std; <br>\r\nint main ( ) <br>\r\n{<img src="images/$img1" style="float:right;"><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int v[100];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int n,i;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"n="; cin>>n;<br>\r\n//se citesc elementele vectorului <br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0;i&#60;n;i++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;{<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"v["&#60;&#60;i&#60;&#60;"]=";<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cin>>v[i];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; int suma=0; <br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0; i&#60;n; i++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;suma=suma+v[i];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60"Suma elementelor vectorului este egala cu:"&#60;&#60;suma; <br>\r\n}\r\n</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Vectori', 'Operatii cu vectori', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(10, 'Produsul elementelor unui vector', '2015-03-27', 'Vladutu Loredana', 'produs94.jpg', 'produsul, elemente, vector', '<p>\r\n#include &#60;iostream&#62 <br>\r\nusing namespace std; <br>\r\nint main ( ) <br>\r\n{<img src="images/$img1" style="float:right;"><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int v[100];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int n,i;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"n="; cin>>n;<br>\r\n//se citesc elementele vectorului <br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0;i&#60;n;i++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;{<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"v["&#60;&#60;i&#60;&#60;"]=";<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cin>>v[i];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; int produs=1; <br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0; i&#60;n; i++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;produs=produs * v[i];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60"Produsul elementelor vectorului este egal cu:"&#60;&#60;produs; <br>\r\n}\r\n</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Vectori', 'Operatii cu vectori', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(11, 'Media aritmetica a elementelor unui vector', '2015-03-27', 'Vladutu Loredana', 'medie89.jpg', 'medie, aritmetica, elemente, vector', '<p>\r\n#include &#60;iostream&#62 <br>\r\nusing namespace std; <br>\r\nint main () <br>\r\n{<img src="images/$img1" style="float:right;"><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int v[100];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int n,i;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"n="; cin>>n;<br>\r\n//se citesc elementele vectorului <br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0;i&#60;n;i++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;{<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"v["&#60;&#60;i&#60;&#60;"]=";<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cin>>v[i];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; int suma=0; <br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0; i&#60;n; i++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;suma=suma+v[i];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60"Suma elementelor vectorului este egala cu:"&#60;&#60;suma&#60;&#60;endl; <br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60"Media aritmetica a elementelor este egala cu:"&#60;&#60;(float) suma/n; \r\n<br>}\r\n</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Vectori', 'Operatii cu vectori', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(12, 'Stergerea unui element egal cu o valoare data x', '2015-03-27', 'Vladutu Loredana', 'nu_gaseste70.jpg', 'stergere, element', '<p>\r\n#include &#60;iostream&#62 <br>\r\nusing namespace std; <br>\r\nint main ( ) <br>\r\n{<img src="images/$img1" style="float:right;"><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int v[100];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int x, n,i;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"n="; cin>>n;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"x="; cin>>x;<br>\r\n//se citesc elementele vectorului <br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0;i&#60;n;i++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;{<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"v["&#60;&#60;i&#60;&#60;"]=";<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cin>>v[i];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int ok=0;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;i=0;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;while(i&#60;n&&!ok)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(x==v[i]) ok=1;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;else i++;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;if(ok==0) cout&#60;&#60;x&#60;&#60;" nu se gaseste in vector. Vectorul ramane neschimbat.";<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;else<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{<img src="images/$img2" style="float:right;"><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for(int j=i;j&#60;=n-2;j++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;v[j]=v[j+1];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;n--;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;"Vectorul dupa operatia de stergere:";<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0;i&#60;n;i++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;v[i]&#60;&#60;" ";<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}\r\n</p>', '', 'gaseste52.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Vectori', 'Operatii cu vectori', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(13, 'Stergerea elementului de pe pozitia k', '2015-03-27', 'Vladutu Loredana', 'pozitia37.jpg', 'stergere, element, pozitia', '<p> \r\n#include &#60;iostream&#62;<br>\r\nusing namespace std;<br>\r\nint main ( )<br>\r\n{<img src="images/$img1" style="float:right;"><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int v[100];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int k, n,i;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;"n="; cin&#62;&#62;n;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;//se citesc elementele vectorului<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0;i&#60;n;i++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;{<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;"v["&#60;&#60;i&#60;&#60;"]=";<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cin&#62;&#62;v[i];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;"Elementele vectorului inainte de stergere:"&#60;&#60;endl;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0;i&#60;n;i++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;v[i]&#60;&#60;" ";<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;endl;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;"Introduceti pozitia k="; cin&#62;&#62;k;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;"Elementele vectorului dupa operatia de stergere:"&#60;&#60;endl;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;for(int j=k-1;j&#60;n;j++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;v[j]=v[j+1];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;n--;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0;i&#60;n;i++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;v[i]&#60;&#60;" ";<br>\r\n}\r\n</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Vectori', 'Operatii cu vectori', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(14, 'Inserarea unui element pe pozitia k', '2015-04-21', 'Vladutu Loredana', 'inserare96.jpg', 'inserare, element, pozitia', '<p> \r\n#include &#60;iostream&#62;<br>\r\nusing namespace std;<br>\r\nint main ( )<br>\r\n{<img src="images/$img1" style="float:right;"><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int v[100];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;int x,k,n,i;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;"n="; cin&#62;&#62;n;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;"k="; cin&#62;&#62;k;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;"x="; cin&#62;&#62;x; //x contine valoarea care se insereaza<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;//se citesc elementele vectorului<br><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0;i&#60;n;i++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;{<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;"v["&#60;&#60;i&#60;&#60;"]=";<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cin&#62;&#62;v[i];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br><br>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"Elementele vectorului inainte de inserare sunt:"&#60;&#60;endl;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0;i&#60;n;i++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;v[i]&#60;&#60;" ";<br><br>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=n;i&#62;k;i--)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;v[i]=v[i-1];<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;v[k-1]=x;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;endl;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout<<"Elementele dupa inserare sunt:"&#60;&#60;endl;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for(i=0;i&#60;=n;i++)<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&#60;&#60;v[i]&#60;&#60;" ";<br>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Vectori', 'Operatii cu vectori', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(15, 'Interclasare', '2015-04-23', 'Vladutu Loredana', 'image28.jpg', 'interclasare', '<p>Se dau doi vectori ordonati crescatori:vectorul <u>a</u> cu <u>n</u> elemente si vectorul <u>b</u> cu <u>m</u> elemente. <br> Sa se construiasca vectorul <u>c</u> care va contine elementele vectorilor <i>a</i> si <i>b</i>, ordonate crescator.<br>Vectorul <u>a</u>: a[0] &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;a[1]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;a[n-1];<br>Vectorul <u>b</u>: b[0]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;b[1]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;...&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;b[m-1] </p>  <br><h3>Algoritmul:</h3>i&larr;0 ; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;j&larr;0; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;k&larr;0; <br>cat timp (i&lt;=n-1 && j&lt;=m-1) executa <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;daca a[i]&lt; b[j] atunci <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;c[k]&larr;a[i] <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;k&larr;k+1 <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;i&larr;i+1 <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;altfel <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;c[k]&larr;b[j] <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;k&larr;k+1 <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;j&larr;j+1 <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sfarsit_daca <br>sfarsit_cat_timp <br><br>daca i&lt;=n-1 atunci <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pentru t&larr;i,n-1 executa <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;c[k]&larr;a[t]<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;k&larr;k+1 <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sfarsit_pentru <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;altfel <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pentru t&larr;j,m-1 executa <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;c[k]&larr;b[t] <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;k&larr;k+1 <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sfarsit_pentru <br>sfarsit_daca <br><h3>Descrierea algoritmului:</h3>Se parcurg simultan cei doi vectori prin intermediul structurii repetetive <b>cat timp</b> si se adauga in vectorul <b>c</b> elementul cel mai mic dintre <b>a[i]</b> si <b>b[j]</b>. <br>La iesirea din structura <b>cat timp</b>, poate exista una dintre urmatoarele situatii: <ol><li> Exista elemente neparcurse din vectorul <b>a</b>(i&lt;=n-1), iar elementele din vectorul au fost adaugate in totalitate in vectorul <b>c</b>.<br>Se adauga elementele <b>a[i]</b>, <b>a[i+1]</b>, ... , <b>a[n-1]</b> in vectorul <b>c</b>. </li><li> Exista elemente neparcurse din vectorul <b>b</b> (j&lt;=m-1), iar elementele din vectorul <b>a</b> au fost adaugate in totalitate in vectorul <b>c</b>.<br>Se adauga elementele <b>b[j]</b>, <b>b[j+1]</b>, ... , <b>b[m-1]</b> in vectorul <b>c</b>.</li></ol><h3>Exemplu: </h3>n=6 <br> <br><img src="images/$img1"> <br>m=8 <br> <br><img src="images/$img2"> <br> <br>i=0 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; j=0&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;k=0 <br>i&lt;=n-1 && j&lt;=m-1 (o&lt;=5 && 0&lt;=7) Adevarat <br>a[i]&lt; b[j] (a[0]&lt; b[0] : 7&lt;6) Fals => c[0]=b[0] => c[0]=6 <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; k=k+1=1; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; j=j+1=1<br><img src="images/$img3"><br><br>i&lt;=n-1 && j&lt;=m-1 (0&lt;=5 && 1&lt;=7) Adevarat <br>a[i]&lt; b[j] (a[0]&lt; b[1] : 7&lt; 10) Adevarat => c[1]=a[0] => c[1]=7<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;k=k+1=2; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;i=i+1=2; <br><img src="images/$img4"><br> <br>i&lt;=n-1 && j&lt;=m-1 (1&lt;=5 && 1&lt;=7) Adevarat<br>a[i]&lt; b[j] (a[1]&lt; b[1] : 15&lt;10) Fals => c[2]=b[1] => c[2]=10 <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; k=k+1=3;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;j=j+1=3; <br><img src="images/$img5"><br> <br>i&lt;=n-1 && j&lt;=m-1 (1&lt;=5 && 2&lt;=7) Adevarat <br>a[i]&lt; b[j] (a[1]&lt; b[2] : 15&lt;12) Fals => c[3]=b[2] => c[3]=12 <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;k=k+1=4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;j=j+1=3; <br><img src="images/$img6"><br> <br>i&lt;=n-1 && j&lt;=m-1 (1&lt;=5 && 3&lt;=7) Adevarat <br>a[i]&lt; b[j] (a[1]&lt; b[3] : 15&lt;16) Adevarat =>c[4]=a[1] => c[4]=15 <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;k=k+1=5;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; i=i+1=2;<br><img src="images/$img7"><br> <br>i&lt;=n-1 && j&lt;=m-1 (2&lt;=5 && 3&lt;=7) Adevarat <br>a[i]&lt; b[j] (a[2]&lt; b[4] : 20&lt;18) Fals => c[6]=b[4] => c[6]=18 <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;k=k+1=6;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;j=j+1=4;<br><img src="images/$img8"><br> <br>i&lt;=n-1 && j&lt;=m-1 (2&lt;=5 && 4&lt;=7) Adevarat <br>a[i]&lt; b[j] (a[2]&lt; b[4] : 20&lt;18) Fals => c[6]=b[4] => c[6]=18<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;k=k+1=7;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;j=j+1=5;<br><img src="images/$img9"><br> <br>i&lt;=n-1 && j&lt;=m-1 (2&lt;=5 && 5&lt;=7) Adevarat <br>a[i]&lt; b[j] (a[2]&lt; b[5] : 20&lt;20) Fals => c[7]=b[5] => c[6]=20<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;k=k+1=8;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;j=j+1=6;<br><img src="images/$img10"><br> <br>i&lt;=n-1 && j&lt;=m-1 (2&lt;=5 && 6&lt;=7) Adevarat <br>a[i]&lt; b[j] (a[2]&lt; b[6] : 20&lt;22) Adevarat => c[8]=a[2] => c[8]=20<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;k=k+1=9;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;i=i+1=3;<br><img src="images/$img11"><br> <br>i&lt;=n-1 && j&lt;=m-1 (3&lt;=5 && 6&lt;=7) Adevarat <br>a[i]&lt; b[j] (a[3]&lt; b[6] : 31&lt;22) Fals => c[9]=b[6] => c[9]=22<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;k=k+1=10;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;j=j+1=7;<br><img src="images/$img12"><br> <br>i&lt;=n-1 && j&lt;=m-1 (3&lt;=5 && 7&lt;=7) Adevarat <br>a[i]&lt; b[j] (a[3]&lt; b[7] : 31&lt;25) Fals => c[10]=b[7] => c[10]=25<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;k=k+1=11;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;j=j+1=8;<br><img src="images/$img13"><br> <br>i&lt;=n-1 && j&lt;=m-1 (3&lt;=5 && 8&lt;=7) Fals<br>Se iese din structura <b> cat timp</b>.<br>Se verifica conditia i&lt;=n-1 (3&lt;=5). Conditia este adevarata; se adauga elementele a[3], a[4],&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a[5] in vectorul <b>c</b> si k=14.<br>La final, vectorul <b>c</b> contine elementele:<br><img src="images/$img14"><br> <br> <br> <BR><div class=test3><B>Programul in C++</B></div><br><textarea rows="10" cols="50" readonly style="color: lightblue; background-color: grey; width: 300px; height: 150px;">  #include <iostream> using namespace std; int main () {int n,m, i, t,j, k, a[100],b[100],c[100];  cout<<"n="; cin>>n;  for(i=0;i<n;i++)    cin>>a[i];  cout<<"m="; cin>>m;  for(j=0;j<m;j++)   cin>>b[j];  i=j=k=0;  while(i<=n-1 && j<=m-1)     if(a[i]<b[j])            c[k++]=a[i++];     else          c[k++]=b[j++];  if(i<=n-1)     for(t=i;t<=n-1;t++)         c[k++]=a[t];  else     for(t=j;t<=m-1;t++)          c[k++]=b[t];  cout<<"Elementele vectorului c sunt:";  for(i=0;i<k;i++)      cout<<c[i]<<" "; return 0; }</textarea>', '', 'interclasare_15_287.jpg', 'interclasare_15_315.jpg', 'interclasare_15_441.jpg', 'interclasare_15_587.jpg', 'interclasare_15_669.jpg', 'interclasare_15_736.jpg', 'interclasare_15_867.jpg', 'interclasare_15_92.jpg', 'interclasare_15_1045.jpg', 'interclasare_15_1186.jpg', 'interclasare_15_1233.jpg', 'interclasare_15_1327.jpg', 'interclasare_15_146.jpg', '', 'Vectori', 'Algoritmi fundamentali de prelucrare a vectorilor', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '');
