(17, 'Operatii cu doua multimi', '2015-04-20', 'Vladutu Loredana', 'Oryx Antelope32.jpg', 'operatii,multimi,doua', '<p>\r\nSe citesc elementele a doua multimi: <br>\r\n-multimea A cu n elemente <br>\r\n-multimea B cu m elemente. <br>\r\nDeterminati: <br>\r\n1. Reuniunea celor doua multimi\r\n<br>\r\n2. Intersectia celor doua multimi\r\n<br>\r\n3. Diferenta celor doua multimi\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>Exemplu:</h4>\r\nA={2, 4, 7, 8, 10} <br>\r\nB={4, 8, 20, 25} <br>\r\nReuniunea: D={2, 4, 7, 8, 10, 20, 25} <br>\r\nIntersectia: C={4, 8} <br>\r\nDiferenta A-B=E={2, 7, 10} <br>\r\nDiferenta B-A=F={20, 25}\r\n</p>', 'Vectori', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
